data.description: Motivated Seller with recent Price Drop! Discover your dream home in this exquisite 3-year-old modern farmhouse on almost 1/3 acre in Fruitland. With a captivating blend of modern convenience and classic farmhouse charm, this property offers an open floorplan flooded with natural light, a gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, and luxurious LVP flooring. The master suite features a walk-in closet and a spa-like walk-in shower. Enjoy outdoor tranquility on the patio and make use of the extra deep 2-car garage. No HOAs or CC&Rs grant you freedom to personalize your space. Located in the heart of Fruitland, this property provides a tranquil lifestyle near essential amenities and major highways. Don't miss your chance to experience comfort, style, and freedom. Schedule a viewing today and embark on the next chapter of your life in this exceptional home.
